{"tid":1467174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過今晚點解機埸發生咁多事","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:30.000Z","uid":167971,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a636b6b2ea3a88b9d4f7545b35ce9b598a73ad4","tid":1467174,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"因為如果機場越亂越多事 <br />\n就會令想入機場嘅和理非越黎越少<br />\n邊個會係最大得益呀???<br />\n嗰班人就係想示威者自亂陣腳 然後柒出國際<br />\n今日咁多個鏡頭影住 如果死咗人會幾難睇呀<br />\n咁多位手足冷靜d <br />\n機場已經係殺手鐧 <br />\n輸埋就玩撚完架喇<br />\n<br />\n至於打FA同記者嗰d人 請好好控制情緒<br />\n你地會令到人懷疑你地係鬼<br />\n從來手足絕對唔會搞FA同記者<br />\n只有PoPo先會<br />\n<br />\n入機場嘅唔好咁易俾人煽動到<br />\n冷靜 冷靜同冷靜"},{"pid":"f648ba84e493187804a41d1b10272cf6e4e1d90a","tid":1467174,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰"},{"pid":"c2a0a62921b3dff3aa7cec8aa5606bcaa77d8247","tid":1467174,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07078482f6848784a3e21fcef2a29f8aa9c5a1a2","tid":1467174,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1da7e2373aac21c3b3464bed8751d98c343608e","tid":1467174,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"302e102439e98eaecfdf56b3218862428d19ac4d","tid":1467174,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b5058c7a519eb3e525e0177f7b7c217254b8dc47","tid":1467174,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"22b607b7d8bbbd983850f51dad7623ffbe404e75","tid":1467174,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"ddc4dbba38e749898c9967f882c4d005